author: thrantal
msg: WICKET-1713: Fixed the case where elements with stored tabIndexes are updated via ajax between opening and closing the ModalWindow. The DOM elements coming from the server don't have the custom property that was set to the instances of the client, so the (usually correct) tabIndex coming from the server must not be overwritten with null.
